          "description": "Professional English for meetings, presentations, negotiations, and cross-cultural communication. Covers opening, interrupting, agreeing, disagreeing, summarizing, following up, and email communication.",
          "terms": [
            {
              "cn": "我们开始吧",
              "en": "let's get started / let's kick things off",
