              "ipa": "wiː niːd jɔːr əˈpruːvl ɒn"
            },
            {
              "cn": "我写信是关于",
              "en": "I'm writing regarding / with reference to",
              "ipa": "aɪm ˈraɪtɪŋ rɪˈɡɑːrdɪŋ"
