              "ipa": "pliːz rɪˈspɒnd baɪ"
            },
            {
              "cn": "感谢您的时间",
              "en": "thank you for your time",
              "ipa": "θæŋk juː fɔːr jɔːr taɪm"
            },
            {
              "cn": "如我理解有误请指正",
              "en": "please correct me if I'm wrong",
              "ipa": "pliːz kəˈrekt miː ɪf aɪm rɒŋ"
